@38203  = ~HOODWINKER OF BARAVAR CLOAKSHADOW: Baravar Cloakshadow, the Sly One, is the gnomish deity of deception and illusions. Clerics of Baravar are known as Hoodwinkers and tend to be the sneakiest of gnomes, who serve their communities by instructing them in disguise and camoflage.

