@76503  = ~CHAOS PRIEST: These seekers of enlightenment take a turn toward what many view as nihilistic: pure chaos.  Chaos Priests claim that all existence - even order itself - can spring from a minute vibration in a simple particle, blossoming into the unexpected: a universe. They indulge and encourage chaos wherever they go, and there must be something to their actions, because by some unknown mechanism, they are granted access to powerful magic. The magic is fickle though, suffering the same uncertainty that plagues Wild Mages. Scholars debate whether their magic is granted by a manipulative deity, or whether they have possibly hit upon some deep structural secret of the multiverse. Whatever the truth, most people view these Occultists with fear and wariness.

